title: Camacho (João Inocencio)
body: He was a native of the parish of Ribeira Brava and died in Funchal in the last quarter of the last century. He distinguished himself as a journalist and was the founder and chief editor of the newspaper Religião e Progresso, which was published in this city in 1879 and 1880.

João Inocencio: Journalist and founder of the newspaper Religião e Progresso
